        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A powerful globe of searing sunlight explodes in the area, dealing 8d10 fire damage to all creatures in the area, plus an additional @Damage[(@item.level+1)d10[vitality]] damage to undead creatures. Each creature in the area must attempt a Reflex save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Blinded] permanently.</p>\n<p>If the globe overlaps with an area of magical darkness, <em>sunburst</em> attempts to counteract the darkness effect.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The fire damage increases by 1d10, and the vitality damage against undead increases by 1d10.</p>"
